After ETC double-spend attacks, the FinanceX team has decided to temporarily suspend transactions for ETC during this time. We would also like to make clear that this is NOT an issue with FinanceX, and rather an issue with the ETC blockchain.  Users who hold ETC will have their balances preserved until we are sure that attacks are not possible. We will announce the reopening of ETC trading when a formal decision is made.  NOTE: During the suspension you will not receive ETC sent to your address. ETC sent during this time will be lost and are not recoverable. Body: SCAM ALERT    There have been many recent attempts to SCAM the FinanceX community by individuals/groups using many different methods.  1) Copying our Facebook page  2) Copying our telegram admin profiles  3) Sending dirty links to obtain personal information  4) Sending of emails to request personal information  Unfortunately, not all of us have the best of intentions. We have to stay alert to the small minority with bad intentions.  So what can you do?  1) Don't trust anyone giving wallet addresses (Image 2)🚧  2) Check the Telegram "admin" has the word admin in the top-right corner of the message (Image 1)🚧  3) Only click on links with a URL that you are familiar with🚧  4) Only trust emails from addresses ending in @financex.io (Image 3 is a fake email)🚧  FinanceX is working hard to eliminate the exposure of our community to such SCAMS  Stay alert!!

Title: [ANN] [ICO]🚩🌎FINANCEX - The next generation exchange|FIAT support🚩🌎
Body: ❤️Hello to our loyal FinanceX community❤️  Thank you for being a part of our community, engaging in discussion, and seeing the huge potential in the FinanceX project and ICO.  FinanceX has added a new round of Presales changing the dates of the ICO.  In order for FinanceX to reach its full potential and give our investors the highest ROI that they deserve, we believe it is necessary to provide more time.  It also gives our Indonesian investors more time to take advantage of the low Presale price before the impending launch of our Indonesian exchange. The launch of our Indonesian exchange will go ahead as planned!  The new ICO dates are as follows:  Presales continue until November 14 ICO Round 1: November 21 - December 4 ICO Round 2: December 5 - December 19 ICO Round 3: December 20 - December 31 FNX listing date: January 15  With the current state of the market, if FinanceX continued with the planned dates, we wouldn't be providing our investors with the best opportunity for profits.  Good teams make the necessary adjustments to be as successful as possible. FinanceX aims to create the biggest exchange in Southeast Asia and among the top 10 in the Asia-Pacific region within 3 years.  FinanceX sincerely apologizes for the inconvenience that the date change may cause to our community and we are happy to answer any questions that you may have.  Given the state of the market, FinanceX has done exceptionally well to all but reach our Private sale hardcap, and experience a good sale rate during the first Presale stage. Investors are identifying the uniqueness of our product.  Relevent documents will be updated in the next 24 hours.  Thank you for your patience and understanding and we are excited to share our current and future success with you!

Author: FinanceX
Title: [ANN] [ICO]🚩🌎FINANCEX - The next generation exchange|FIAT support🚩🌎
Body: There are many advantages to using the FinanceX exchange.  1) Fiat-to-coin trading pairs - this allows traders in countries outside of the US easy access to the coins they desire and allows traders to cash-out directly to their local currency without the need for intermediates. 2) Rapid assets transfers - transferring from bank-to-wallet takes less than 3 minutes and from wallet-to-bank less than one hour. Much faster than the competition. 3) Low fees - 0.3% for trading fees and no fees for transferring assets between exchanges 4) Easy-to-use interface - intuative and user friendly interface making trading easy 5) Rapid processing - Our trading core, built off of the trading core of the Hanoi Stock Exchange, can process up to 100,000 transactions per second 6) Interexchange network - we will create a network of exchanges starting in Southeast Asia and expanding. The first was recntly launched in Vietnam and more will be launched before the end of this year in Indonesia, Malaysia and the Philippines. 7) Our FNX token - It will boost liquidity on our platform   Most ICO's are pitched on an idea rather than a product. We have a high quality product and we have no trouble listing our token as we have the exchange!!

Author: FinanceX
Title: [ANN] [ICO]🚩🌎FINANCEX - The next generation exchange|FIAT support🚩🌎
Body: I thought you were going to ask a tough question!   There are many advantages to using the FinanceX exchange.  1) Fiat-to-coin trading pairs - this allows traders in countries outside of the US easy access to the coins they desire and allows traders to cash-out directly to their local currency without the need for intermediates. 2) Rapid assets transfers - transferring from bank-to-wallet takes less than 3 minutes and from wallet-to-bank less than one hour. Much faster than the competition. 3) Low fees - 0.3% for trading fees and no fees for transferring assets between exchanges 4) Easy-to-use interface - intuative and user friendly interface making trading easy 5) Rapid processing - Our trading core, built off of the trading core of the Hanoi Stock Exchange, can process up to 100,000 transactions per second 6) Interexchange network - we will create a network of exchanges starting in Southeast Asia and expanding. The first was recntly launched in Vietnam and more will be launched before the end of this year in Indonesia, Malaysia and the Philippines. 7) Our FNX token - It will boost liquidity on our platform   Most ICO's are pitched on an idea rather than a product. We have a high quality product and we have no trouble listing our token as we have the exchange!!  Thanks for the question.

Body: Absolutely, but these things happen one step at a time. Our first priority is the Southeast Asian market before expanding in to the wider Asia-Pacific region. The fiats you mentioned are most definitely on our radar in the not so distant future.  Thanks for the question. I hope this helps!

Author: FinanceX
Title: [ANN] [ICO]🚩🌎FINANCEX - The next generation exchange|FIAT support🚩🌎
Body: Good question! Many things!  1) We provide customers with fiat-to-coin trading pairs allowing quick and easy cash-out and enabling traders to bypass BTC if they wish.  2) Low trading fees. It is not uncommon to see trading fees set at 1-2%, yet we only charge 0.3% and there are no hidden fees.  3) We offer transparency. Just as our fees are transparent, we want our team and our vision to be completely transparent. We plan to do this with our growing social media presence.  4) Real-time automatic trading capable of processing up to 100,000 thousand transactions per second. Most exchanges use the OTC model which is less transparent, more risky and much slower.  5) High liquidity. Once established, our platform will offer high liquidity as we set up an interexchange network between Southeast Asian countries. Our FNX token will aid in high liquidity.  6) Rapid processing times. Bank-to-wallet transfers will take less than 3 minutes and wallet-to-bank less than 1 hour. Much faster than competitors.   Hope this helps!!!

We won't stop there. Singapore, Thailand, Laos, and Myanmar are in the plan, but if the right conditions present themselves, we will also look further afield.

Author: FinanceX
Title: [ANN] [ICO]🚩🌎FINANCEX - The next generation exchange|FIAT support🚩🌎
Body: ★ ICO WEBSITE ★ FINANCEX EXCHANGE ★ WHITEPAPER ★ TELEGRAM ★ TELE-GROUP for VN ★ ★ FACEBOOK ★ TWITTER ★ LINKEDIN ★ REDDIT ★ MEDIUM ★ YOUTUBE ★ STEEMIT ★    1. Problems : There are many crypto exchanges existing in the world, but most of them only support coin-to-coin trading. Those have 3 main disadvantages: -   High fees -   Time consuming: you'll need BTC or ETH before purchasing the cryptocurrency you want. -   Risky: crypto market is so volatile and the rates change very quickly. You may not get the exchange rate you want.  There are a few exchanges that allow you to trade using fiat, but they still have limitations: -   High trading fees (1-2%) -   Poor technology makes the trading process slow with low availability. This prevent you from maximizing your potential profits. -   Low liquidity. Difficult to find a buyer.    2. Our solution :  FinanceX is developed to solve all of those problems:  FinanceX allows users to trade directly from crypto to fiat and vice versa. You only need to transfer money from your bank account to the FinanceX exchange then you can buy any crypto you want. -   Simple payment method: We provide customers with a range of payment methods. -   High speed: our trading core is being based on Forex trading core with real-time matching ability which can proceed hundreds of thousands of orders per second. -   High liquidity: we will create an interexchange network between countries in the Asia Pacific region. -   Simple to trade: Modern, intuitive user interface and a simple order process so you can easily trade even if you are beginner. -   Security and Privacy: secure information and keep money in your wallet during the transaction. -   Low trading fees: competitive treatments and costs compared to other platforms in each countries. -   Transparent Fees Structure:  No hidden fee and we only charge for what are stated clearly in the Fee Structure document You can find out more in : https://support.financex.io/faq/fee-trading-on-financex/  3.
